798023da-f301-4f1b-891b-180386c8066e.title: Joe
798023da-f301-4f1b-891b-180386c8066e.text: Hi, I'm Joe, door guard for Lady Keli.

2a7c483e-cc1a-46e7-9d5f-3e012bd2d04c.title: <player>
2a7c483e-cc1a-46e7-9d5f-3e012bd2d04c.text: Hi, who are you guarding here?

9c1f1080-470f-446d-b853-ae165e09f368.title: Joe
9c1f1080-470f-446d-b853-ae165e09f368.text:
Can't say, all very secret. You should get out of here.
I am not supposed to talk while I guard.

f08b568e-e553-448b-ac32-964b4ae682c3.title: Joe
f08b568e-e553-448b-ac32-964b4ae682c3.text: Hi, I'm Joe, door guard for Lady Keli.

1af45e10-00e0-4c37-a778-cb01cc93f970.title: <player>
1af45e10-00e0-4c37-a778-cb01cc93f970.text: Hi, who are you guarding here?

31e54584-3097-425c-a183-d690cc75b9db.title: Joe
31e54584-3097-425c-a183-d690cc75b9db.text:
Can't say, all very secret. You should get out of here.
I am not supposed to talk while I guard.

options.text: I have some beer here, fancy one?
Tell me about the life of a guard.
What did you want to be when you were a boy?
I had better leave, I don't want trouble.

836c3ee6-d442-42c0-ab35-758ad79d372d.title: Joe
836c3ee6-d442-42c0-ab35-758ad79d372d.text:
Ah, that would be lovely, just one now,
just to wet my throat.

dcbf5e0c-dd31-4e20-a581-4338c67e36da.title: <player>
dcbf5e0c-dd31-4e20-a581-4338c67e36da.text: I have some beer here, fancy one?

f9b800b0-497e-4ff1-a369-ff22bfa2d01d.title: <player>
f9b800b0-497e-4ff1-a369-ff22bfa2d01d.text: Of course, it must be tough being here without a drink.

043b1dbe-f787-4b6f-93da-d35d6a7b4e91.text: You hand the guard a beer.

3b46a8e2-c942-4769-a223-4ddebaf4c608.text:
The guard seems tipsy, perhaps more beer
will cause him to blackout for a moment.

8a99b095-a2a7-48b2-ae33-a40302937864.title: Joe
8a99b095-a2a7-48b2-ae33-a40302937864.text: That was perfect, I can't thank you enough.

3fce7e0d-467b-49c8-bb72-15af39e8019f.title: <player>
3fce7e0d-467b-49c8-bb72-15af39e8019f.text: How are you? Still ok? Not too drunk?

9501a354-c2b1-497e-af02-c04ee33cd3f9.title: <player>
9501a354-c2b1-497e-af02-c04ee33cd3f9.text: Would you care for another, my friend?

8a7ed526-f519-43bd-ba54-309d286210d5.title: Joe
8a7ed526-f519-43bd-ba54-309d286210d5.text: I better not, I don't want to be drunk on duty.

4565b3f2-59b5-414f-8615-7918d3aa776c.title: <player>
4565b3f2-59b5-414f-8615-7918d3aa776c.text:
Here, just keep these for later,
I hate to see a thirsty guard.

07c538ae-7db0-4464-80d3-6438e4979892.text:
You hand the guard two more beers, he quickly downs
them one after the other in front of you.

f412c583-c584-46a7-9c9f-12ecddb1d5eb.title: Joe
f412c583-c584-46a7-9c9f-12ecddb1d5eb.text:
Franksh, that wash just what I need to shtay on guard.
No more beersh, I don't want to get drunk.

19a9972f-8474-4906-9dd6-5be078325c2a.title: <player>
19a9972f-8474-4906-9dd6-5be078325c2a.text: Tell me about the life of a guard.

ff16866a-7528-4779-9afa-02383c3345dc.title: Joe
ff16866a-7528-4779-9afa-02383c3345dc.text:
.... But most of those hours are a drag. If only I had
spent more time in Knight school when I was a young
boy. Maybe I wouldn't be here now, scared of Keli.

options.text: Hey, chill out, I won't cause you trouble.
What did you want to be when you were a boy?
I had better leave, I don't want trouble.

8e74cea4-638b-44da-9fb2-9ffabb719e59.title: <player>
8e74cea4-638b-44da-9fb2-9ffabb719e59.text:
Hey, chill out, I won't cause you trouble. I was just
wondering what you do to relax.

85da320a-60c8-406f-95a5-0e1889af9d9a.title: Joe
85da320a-60c8-406f-95a5-0e1889af9d9a.text:
You never relax with these people, but it's a good
career for a young man and some of the shouting I
rather like.

options.text: So what do you buy with these great wages?
Tell me about the life of a guard.
Would you be interested in making a little more money?
I had better leave, I don't want trouble.

70465a1d-817f-4133-af7a-79c2757e2eaf.title: <player>
70465a1d-817f-4133-af7a-79c2757e2eaf.text: So what do you buy with these great wages?

d443aa26-d0d5-4b6a-9554-50b475c22423.title: Joe
d443aa26-d0d5-4b6a-9554-50b475c22423.text:
Really, after working here, there's only time for a drink
or three. All us guards go to the same bar and drink
ourselves stupid.

de77f3bb-bed4-45f2-8045-f4d9eb208891.title: Joe
de77f3bb-bed4-45f2-8045-f4d9eb208891.text:
It's what I enjoy these days, that fade into
unconsciousness. I can't resist the sight of
a really cold beer.

options.text: Tell me about the life of a guard.
What did you want to be when you were a boy?
I had better leave, I don't want trouble.

9422afd5-649c-4495-9dbb-1421d0c2cafc.title: <player>
9422afd5-649c-4495-9dbb-1421d0c2cafc.text: What did you want to be when you were a boy?

d3c7847c-7dba-460b-a883-9cd227e5da6b.title: Joe
d3c7847c-7dba-460b-a883-9cd227e5da6b.text:
Well, I loved to sit by the lake, with my toes in the
water and shoot the fish with my bow and arrow.

a0b08e8b-40dc-4f25-8b8a-604f74e7dc2b.title: <player>
a0b08e8b-40dc-4f25-8b8a-604f74e7dc2b.text: That was a strange hobby for a little boy.

58840625-91b4-49b4-a4ed-b6d7738692e2.title: Joe
58840625-91b4-49b4-a4ed-b6d7738692e2.text:
It kept us from goblin hunting, which was what most
boys did. What are you here for?

options.text: Chill out, I won't cause you trouble.
Tell me about the life of a guard.
I had better leave, I don't want trouble.

37914213-ba78-4654-bbd1-a5585b22848e.title: <player>
37914213-ba78-4654-bbd1-a5585b22848e.text: I had better leave, I don't want trouble.

2ac69ff8-7eac-4fb2-8a61-f611849cdaf7.title: Joe
2ac69ff8-7eac-4fb2-8a61-f611849cdaf7.text:
Thanks, I appreciate that. Talking on duty can be
punishable by having your mouth stitched up.
These are tough people, no mistake.

6b2a079d-e2a3-43f8-9035-54f3d4948b0d.title: <player>
6b2a079d-e2a3-43f8-9035-54f3d4948b0d.text:
Would you be interested in making a little more
money?

8a0df5b2-c926-4f9f-9f7e-59331f8a1f77.title: Joe
8a0df5b2-c926-4f9f-9f7e-59331f8a1f77.text:
WHAT?! Are you trying to bribe me? I may not be a
great guard, but I am loyal. How DARE you try to
bribe me!

d1ee5487-34e7-4eab-a2ad-6479c5d2de54.title: <player>
d1ee5487-34e7-4eab-a2ad-6479c5d2de54.text:
No, no, you got the wrong idea, totally. I just
wondered if you wanted some part-time bodyguard
work.

b7a48124-dcb8-4cf7-a052-ddbfc2a23682.title: <player>
b7a48124-dcb8-4cf7-a052-ddbfc2a23682.text:
Oh. Sorry. No, I don't need money. As long as you
were not offering me a bribe.

c45b6a1f-5848-43c9-bc1e-606ad829edc9.title: Joe
c45b6a1f-5848-43c9-bc1e-606ad829edc9.text: Halt! Who goes there? Friend or foe?

736348cd-6b78-408a-a0c7-9ac71b6782b2.title: <player>
736348cd-6b78-408a-a0c7-9ac71b6782b2.text: Hi friend, I am just checking out things here.

05080a11-e1ef-46c9-9760-f8f9a8059505.title: Joe
05080a11-e1ef-46c9-9760-f8f9a8059505.text:
The Prince got away, I am in trouble. I better not talk
to you, they are not sure I was drunk.

6d2dcce2-663c-43f1-a2e7-a492be54c33c.title: <player>
6d2dcce2-663c-43f1-a2e7-a492be54c33c.text: I won't say anything, your secret is safe with me.
